i've been looking for a solid <span class="highlighted">happy hour</span> place in silverlake, and by george, i think i've done it! &nbsp;covertly located on the busiest strip of hyperion ave, amongst other stand-out eateries like barbarella and lucky duck, i've driven past it many times without noticing it's existence. &nbsp; they boast a great selection of libations and the food is everything i have ever hoped for in a gastropub. &nbsp;the interior is dark and moody, with lots of wood and deep colors. &nbsp;there are large tables for big groups as well as booths for more intimate get-togethers. &nbsp;the front area is more like a gastropub and the back room has more of a bar feel. &nbsp;it is loud enough that i can burst into inebriated laughter without disturbing the peace and getting the stink eye, but still quiet enough that i can have a serious conversation with a good friend. the food, as i previously mentioned, is awesome. &nbsp;some stand out items on the <span class="highlighted">happy hour</span> menu are:-lettuce cups: &nbsp;divine. &nbsp;the meat to lettuce ratio is commendable and the cilantro garnish and slaw adds a wonderful element of freshness and texture. &nbsp;the meat is incredibly flavorful and tender, like a nugget of the best marinated korean barbeque your imagination can fathom.-fried chicken sandwich: delish. well spiced , light breading and huge. &nbsp;i could tell the chicken breast was freshly breaded and fried.-chicken wings: omg. tantilizing. spicy is definitely spicy. &nbsp;they have other exotic flavors like thai and blueberry. &nbsp;definitely fresh and succulent. &nbsp;served with a side of ranch (so fresh, i could taste the herbs) or blue cheese.the drinks are also unique and delicous. &nbsp;the spicy greyhound is a specialty cocktail on the <span class="highlighted">happy hour</span> menu and it is sweet and refreshing with a nice, unexpected kick from the jalapeno. try it. the service here is fantastic! &nbsp;the servers are attentive and amiable. &nbsp;the food comes out with adequate speed and drinks are refilled graciously. &nbsp;i look forward to broadening my hyperion public experience and coming back for dinner.
