ifically their cookies and unicorn gluten-free cake! the decor is something to marvel over, and i love how the front of the restaurant is exposed to the street through large openings. and, although i haven't ventured in yet for it, and am not deterred by my two not so exceptional experiences, they do have free hors d'oeuvres during <span class="highlighted">happy hour</span> (4pm-7pm, mon-fri)!
